org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class DConRefRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.RecordBase
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.Record
        • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.StandardRecord
          • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.DConRefRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public class DConRefRecord
extends StandardRecord
    DConRef records specify a range in a workbook (internal or external) that serves as a data source for pivot tables or data consolidation. Represents a DConRef Structure [MS-XLS s. 2.4.86], and the contained DConFile structure [MS-XLS s. 2.5.69]. This in turn contains a XLUnicodeStringNoCch [MS-XLS s. 2.5.296]. 
             _______________________________
        |          DConRef              |
(bytes) +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+-+
        |    ref    |cch|  stFile   | un|
        +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+-+
                              |
                     _________|_____________________
                    |DConFile / XLUnicodeStringNoCch|
                    +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+
             (bits) |h|   reserved  |      rgb      |
                    +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+
    Where
    • DConFile.h = 0x00 if the characters inrgb are single byte, and DConFile.h = 0x01 if they are double byte.

      If they are double byte, then

      • If it exists, the length of DConRef.un = 2. Otherwise it is 1.
      • The length of DConFile.rgb = (2 * DConRef.cch). Otherwise it is equal to DConRef.cch.
    • DConRef.rgb starts with 0x01 if it is an external reference, and with 0x02 if it is a self-reference.
    At the moment this class is read-only.    (DConRef记录指定工作簿（内部或外部）中的一个范围，用作数据透视表或数据整合的数据源。表示DConRef结构[MS-XLS s. 2.4.86]，以及包含的DConFile结构[MS-XLS s. 2.5.69]。这反过来又包含XLUnicodeStringNoCch [MS-XLS s. 2.5.296]。 _______________________________ | DConref | （字节）+-+-+.+-+ | ref |CCH| st文件 | 联合国| +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+-+ | _________|_____________________ |DConFile / XLUnicodeStringNoCch| +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+ （位）|H| 保留| RGB | +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+...+-+-+-+ 其中，如果rGB中的字符是单字节，则DConFile. h = 0x 00;如果字符是双字节，则DConFile. h = 0x 01。如果它们是双字节，那么如果存在，则DConRef.un的长度= 2。否则就是1。DConFile. rgi的长度=（2 * DConRef.cch）。否则等于DConRef. cch。如果是外部引用，DConRef. rnb从0x 01开始，如果是自引用，则从0x 02开始。目前该课程是只读的。)

        protected void serialize(LittleEndianOutput out)
        Description copied from class: StandardRecord
        Write the data content of this BIFF record. The 'ushort sid' and 'ushort size' header fields have already been written by the superclass.

        The number of bytes written must equal the record size reported by RecordBase.getRecordSize()} minus four ( record header consisting of a 'ushort sid' and 'ushort reclength' has already been written by their superclass).

        (写入此BIFF记录的数据内容。超类已经编写了“ushort sid”和“ushort size”标头字段。写入的字节数必须等于RecordBase报告的记录大小。getRecordSize（）}减四（由“ushort sid”和“ushort reclong”组成的记录头已由其超类写入）。)
